 />\n店鋪俾唔到貨我<br />\n我話成張單退<br />\n都叫唔合理？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"咁你開左個 router 用又點退呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"樓主個時序係咪兩樣野一齊買<br />\n部機就要等<br />\n但router就現貨有拎左<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁開左嚟用又正常喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"159ca355d55ec54011d39d513d57589bd11edea5","tid":2402182,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:39:20.000Z","msg":"由於友和令到我好不滿<br />\n所以我一早決定去消委會投訴佢<br />\n雖然消委會都係廢<br />\n但煩下友和，整花下佢個底都好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SPGg4SD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSPGg4SD.png&h=c0c72bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2月10號網上填表投訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔左一個多月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月18號終於覆我啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2yvpTa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2yvpTa.png&h=d0f8e3b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2BT66w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2BT66w.png&h=19dca642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消委會將友和個email attach埋俾我<br />\n睇下覆得幾垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我即係reply佢email<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqWg4TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqWg4TC.png&h=8554263a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到今日消委會打俾我<br />\n問我會唔會有咩野方案可以提供去和解<br />\n心諗 <br />\n點解唔係友和提供<br />\n要我提供呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULWAA0R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULWAA0R.png&h=bbd31c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好 我再用書面回覆多一次<br />\n<br />\n利申：以上用黎紀錄，for將來其他受害者參考<br />\n有後續會再更新"}}